44?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 18 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p></p><p>这张专辑还收录了 B 面歌曲，包括《Androgynous Girls》和《History》、对他们的热门歌曲进行了罕见的电视表演编辑，以及一系列来自那个时代的混音翻唱，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">Blondie</a>的《Hanging On The Telephone》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">Chaka Khan</a>的《I》 “我是每个女人”。</p><p>该专辑将首次推出黑胶唱片，可作为天蓝色 LP 和限量版 D2C 独​​家图片光盘购买。</p><p> 3CD 曲目列表也可在所有平台上通过流媒体和数字方式收听。</p><p> Girls Aloud 宣布将于 11 月进行现场回归，并于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girls-aloud-announce-2024-uk-ireland-arena-tour-3547047">2024 年进行英国和爱尔兰舞台巡演</a>。</p><p>这次演出将在五月和六月举行，被描述为“庆祝 Girls Aloud 丰富的过往曲目以及她们作为乐队所取得的突破性成功。” </p><figure id="attachment_3573015" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3573015" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3573015" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion.jpg" alt="纳丁·科伊尔、金伯利·沃尔什、尼古拉·罗伯茨和谢丽尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/girls-aloud-reunion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3573015" class="wp-caption-text"> BBC 广播 2 台的纳丁·科伊尔、金伯利·沃尔什、尼古拉·罗伯茨和谢丽尔宣布《Girls Aloud》将于 2023 年 11 月 23 日在英国伦敦回归（图片来源：Neil Mockford/GC Images）</figcaption></figure><p>您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girls-aloud-add-extra-shows-to-2024-uk-reunion-arena-tour-3551279">在此处找到完整的日期列表</a>，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fgirls-aloud-tickets%2Fartist%2F999843" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girls-aloud-promise-magic-tour-shows-not-the-same-without-sarah-harding-3550758">乐队向歌迷承诺，这次巡演将是“神奇的”</a> ，但又补充说，如果没有已故乐队成员莎拉·哈丁（Sarah Harding），巡演将“永远不一样”，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/sarah-harding-girls-aloud-obituary-tribute-3038184">于 2021 年因乳腺癌去世</a>。</p><p>谢丽尔告诉<a href="https://news.sky.com/story/girls-aloud-promise-a-magic-reunion-tour-but-say-shows-will-never-be-the-same-without-sarah-13018160" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>天空新闻：</em></a> “一切都不会再一样了，我们接受这一点，但我们将在她的参与下创造出一种新型的光芒。”</p><p>该乐队此前透露，哈丁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girls-aloud-reveal-late-sarah-harding-suggested-they-reform-following-cancer-diagnosis-3547820">在与癌症作斗争期间建议他们有一天会进行改革</a>，但也表示他们没有发行新音乐的计划。</p><p> “我们不能，因为莎拉不会被纳入这种新鲜事物中，”谢丽尔说。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girls-aloud-announce-deluxe-reissue-of-what-will-the-neighbours-say-on-cd-and-vinyl-3572979">《Girls Aloud》宣布豪华再版《邻居会说什么？》 CD 和黑胶唱片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Talking Heads 的《Stop Making Sense》将再次重返影院https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-stop-making-sense-is-returning-to-cinemas-again-3572947?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=talking-heads-stop-making-感觉再次回归电影院Tom SkinnerThu, 18 Jan 2024 11:14:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3572947 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·伯恩 (David Byrne) 出演 Talking Heads 1984 年演唱会电影《Stop Making Sense》" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该电影的收藏版蓝光光盘将在放映时购买</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-stop-making-sense-is-returning-to-cinemas-again-3572947">Talking Heads 的《Stop Making Sense》再次回归影院的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·伯恩 (David Byrne) 出演 Talking Heads 1984 年演唱会电影《Stop Making Sense》" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/RMMBE1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a>的经典音乐会电影<em>《Stop Making Sense》</em>将重返影院。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/talking-heads-stop-making-sense-documentary-is-returning-to-cinemas-after-39-years-3414795">A24 在大银幕上发布了这部 1984 年电影的 4K 重制版，</a>以纪念其成立 40 周年。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-talking-heads-reunite-for-the-first-time-in-20-years-q-and-a-stop-making-sense-3496454">作为 2023 年多伦多国际电影节的一部分，这支标志性乐队还在一场特别放映中重聚</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/concert-films-taylor-swift-eras-talking-heads-beyonce-renaissance-3531888">音乐会电影如何成为大生意（再次）</a></strong></li></ul><p>现在，已确认改编版的<em>《Stop Making Sense》</em>将于下周六（1 月 27 日）重返各地电影院。</p><p> A24 昨天（1 月 17 日）在社交媒体上发帖称，计划在伦敦、纽约、洛杉矶、奥斯汀、芝加哥、旧金山和多伦多等“选定城市”进行“每月住院筛查”。</p><p>此外，粉丝们还可以在每次放映时购买<em>《Stop Making Sense》</em>的珍藏版蓝光光盘以及新的特别商品。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://tickets.stopmakingsense.movie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里购买门票并了解更多信息</a>，并查看下面的公告。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2Nd44nRl33/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div s